<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Manager Request Approved</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Manager Request Approved</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= username %>,</p>
    <p>We are pleased to inform you that your request to become a manager has been approved.</p>
    <p>You can now access additional management features on the platform.</p>
    <p>Thank you for your contributions!</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact support.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
